************************************     Add Credit Card *********************************************

Add credit card test1 - Payment information middle nav
1. Go to development.ariat.com
2. Close subscription
3. Choose RU
4. Go to Sign in
5. Enter user name & password
6. Press login Button
7. Click "ADD" in Payment Information section - My Account page
8. Enter card nickname, name on card, select type card as VISA, enter number, security code, select expiration month & year
9. Press "Apply" button
10. Check the credit card was created in Payment information page
11. Go to My account
12. Click logout 

Add credit card test2 - Payment information left nav
1. Go to development.ariat.com
2. Close subscription
3. Choose RU
4. Go to Sign in
5. Enter user name & password
6. Press login Button
7. Click on Payment Information left navigation
8. Press "Add a credit card"
9. Enter card nickname, name on card, select type card as MASTER CARD, enter number, security code, select expiration month & year
10. Press "Apply" button
11. Go to My account
12. Click logout 

